DecimalRange?","doc":"Get decimal digit range\n\nIf the character is part of a contiguous sequence representing the ten\ndecimal digits in order from 0 to 9, this function returns the first and\nlast characters from this range.\n\nUnicode properties:\n  `Numeric_Type=Decimal`\n  `Numeric_Value` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getDecimalRange?\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">getDecimalRange?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">char</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/92e7648d19f24127919bcf3ff86eb0a43388824c/UnicodeBasic.lean#L723-L737","name":"Unicode.isDecimal","line":723,"kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDecimal","doc":"Check if character represents a decimal digit\n\nFor this property, a character must be part of a contiguous sequence\nrepresenting the ten decimal digits in order from 0 to 9.\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Decimal` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDecimal\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">isDecimal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">char</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},